f-regulatory body must publish a verification framework detailing measures to ensure games are not against public interest, along with other relevant conditions.\n\nThis lifecycle ensures that online real money games are vetted and monitored for compliance with legal and regulatory standards, fostering a safe and fair gaming environment.",
