rified as permissible by the self-regulatory body.\n\n7. **Framework Publication**: The self-regulatory body must also publish a framework for verifying online real money games, which includes measures to ensure that the games are not against the interests of the public.\n\nThis lifecycle ensures that online real money games are regularly assessed for compliance and that relevant information is transparently shared with the public.",
